Package: mtcr-apply
Version: 1.1.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: openjdk-21
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://t.me/NullRE_Channel
Description: MTCR Patch Application Tool for Android APKs
 mtcr-apply is a tool to apply .mtcr patch files to APKs,
 inspired by git-apply. Uses patches generated by MT Manager
 for modifying and patching Android applications.
